fields.name: Piyush Saxena
fields.subject: Feedback- Open Database (EV charging and Swapping Stations)
fields.message:
This is in regard with the Open database (EV charging and Swapping Stations) that has been uploaded on the website stating that it shows EV charging stations in NCT of Delhi. However, out of the 447 EV charging stations provided in the excel sheet, only 74% are actually located within NCT of Delhi. 329 charging stations are available in Delhi whereas 123 from Noida and 5 from Gurgaon has been added in the sheet. 
You may consider updating the sheet for future reference so that it shows a clear picture of available charging infrastructure in Delhi. 
Regards, 
Piyush Saxena

fields.name: Pawan Kumar
fields.description: The SUN Mobility's vision is to create a universal network of interoperable energy infrastructure to accelerate mass adoption of electric mobility. The revolutionary digitally enabled ‘Pay-as-you-go’ system for battery usage offers an extremely convenient way to refuel EVs, thus fostering adoption.
